explanations.reason: The paper focuses on a cross-sectional study examining the prevalence and factors associated with depression and anxiety symptoms among Bangladeshi graduates. The methods used include face-to-face interviews, semi-structured questionnaires, Chi-square tests, and logistic regression analysis with SPSS software. There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models in the title or abstract. The study is purely based on statistical analysis and does not involve any of the listed machine learning or deep learning keywords.
